:<font size="15">יצר</font></div>

===Pronunciation===
יצר / yâtsar / yaw-tsar'

===Etymology===
probably identical with {{HH|3334}} (through the squeezing into shape); (compare {{HH|3331}}); 

===Verb===
'''יצר'''

# To mould into a form; especially as a potter; figuratively to determine (that is, form a resolution): -  X earthen, fashion, form, frame, make (-r), potter, purpose.

